    <p>{`As many of you know my favorite past-time/hobby/etc. is designing the lights for theatre shows (over this winter break I‚Äôll be volunteering at the SLOLT ACT (children‚Äôs) production of The Lion Witch `}{`&`}{` the Wardrobe :D). It is actually one of the main reasons I got in to electrical engineering! So for my senior project I am going to take the idea of designing ‚Äúlights‚Äù a little more literal and try actually design my own lighting fixture!`}</p>
